n Neighbors: Be kind to neighbors, regardless of religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Mujahid reported: We were with Abdullah ibn Amr while his servant prepared to distribute a sheep. Abdullah said, \u201cYoung man, when you are finished, then begin with our Jewish neighbor.\u201d A man said, \u201cJewish? May Allah correct you!\u201d Abdullah said, \u201cI heard the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2943,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/18\/people-wish-death-hour\/","url_meta":{"origin":8048,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Trials: People wish for death before the Hour","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Hour will not be established until a man passes by the grave of another man and he says: Would that I were in his place!\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7115, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 157 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1989,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/23\/best-neighbor-companion\/","url_meta":{"origin":8048,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Neighbors: The best neighbor is best to his neighbors","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"